{"tid":1478282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊岳橋！郭榮鏗！美國參與《香港人權與民主法案會議》","createTime":"2019-08-16T12:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T02:05:47.000Z","uid":81882,"like":98,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"a261265704bbae89466f8e28379f4f5e7a890fdf","tid":1478282,"uid":81882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"相信應該大家都知道呢件事啦，都推一推先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實琴晚已經想開定但唔記得左<br />\n<br />\n首先再講講咩係<br />\n《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n<br />\n係2016年時，香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒到訪美國國會，並會見國會及行政當局中國委員會主席克里斯&middot;史密斯（Chris Smith）、聯席主席魯比奧（Marco Rubio）、參議員科頓（Tom Cotton）等國會人員會面。會議後魯比奧和科頓宣佈會提出「香港人權與民主法案」。<br />\n而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong>是美方對涉及鎮壓基本自由的香港或中國大陸的政府官員，設立懲罰機制，包括禁止涉事官員入境美國及凍結其在美國之資產。<br />\n<br />\n但16年後，靜左一排，直到早排G20團隊同大家既努力，令到美國再行動！<br />\n以上COPY至Wikipedia<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實今次 楊岳橋議員 同 郭榮鏗議員 兩位，<br />\n今次到紐約如無意外係會有三場活動！<br />\n<br />\n第一場<br />\n就係美國時間15/8 所參加左由 亞洲協會(ASIA SOCIERY)所舉辦既 EVENT - Perspective on Hong Kong's Protests<br />\n<br />\n即似以下呢段，同應該好多巴打都睇過既片段<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CLYnTTGWT6Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCLYnTTGWT6Y&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0cTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=78b4caa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CLYnTTGWT6Y</a><br />\n<br />\n第二場<br />\n美國時間 17/8 星期六<br />\n會參加美國當地港人發起既遊行(原野餐)，<br />\n遊行前都會發言！遊行後都有小組討論<br />\n起點：華埠孔子大廈孔子像<br />\n終點：曼哈頓橋小公園<br />\n<br />\n第三場<br />\n下星期，會到 美國眾議院 同議員商討法案<br />\n<br />\n唔知將來如果成事&hellip;有幾多狗官會享受到呢條法案，忘記美國一切，感受大灣區呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國巴打一齊努力！<br />\n<br />\n所以！見大家話佢地特登唔提雙普或漏左重要既野<br />\n唔緊要！仲有機會！<br />\n<br />\n香港加油！"},{"pid":"e55e21b2934a998ec2fce69c7d0bd660b6595051","tid":1478282,"uid":81882,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:32:55.000Z","msg":"大家818今日見！<br />\n<br />\n美國今朝(香港既琴日)<br />\n都有遊行！(又有班0.5搞事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oUbUfrQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoUbUfrQ.jpg&h=cdf2e4a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NY4HK/videos/412288786303022?s=672512884&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNY4HK%2Fvideos%2F412288786303022%3Fs%3D672512884%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0cTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=2f2d86ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NY4HK/videos/412288786303022?s=672512884&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊加油！"},{"pid":"1cc30eb3d2b439212f913441726832ff4dccd93b","tid":1478282,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山 各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f339d2374aff0027bc81798008faf52702ac23e","tid":1478282,"uid":28451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:36:21.000Z","msg":"[香港淡奶] 屬於香港人嘅Timeline上線喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"86ff19d4efb3ce1d10b1c13d3d3d39218128985b","tid":1478282,"uid":156913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"要呼籲埋美國盟國都立呢D法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得美國立, 佢走去英國, 瑞士, 要西方文明都立, 佢地先可以共享大灣區榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a5c4a6497eaa2b7be563de5f2a6d257bf8c2f1","tid":1478282,"uid":83131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1aa0175b6d4a33418590f2c58b73e6a2de5d7b28","tid":1478282,"uid":43468,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YaUGVxy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYaUGVxy.jpg&h=1843bfd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c4afe765023fa06c623f23a9e3e2693f562edb0","tid":1478282,"uid":105905,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:51:47.000Z","msg":"以前做錯既可以而家唔清算住,但今次一定要做得正確"},{"pid":"54112b76bc3b2683ff20d98b1c9c80dac6001d2a","tid":1478282,"uid":134071,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"1aa0175b6d4a33418590f2c58b73e6a2de5d7b28","tid":1478282,"uid":43468,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YaUGVxy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYaUGVxy.jpg&h=1843bfd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"[轉貼] FACT CHECKED<br />\n圖中內容有嚴重錯誤<br />\n<br />\n1. 根據議事規則第46條有關表決的部份<br />\n議案通過係需要在席表決的議員過半數贊成<br />\n因此在席棄權絕非「與贊成無異」<br />\n反而係「與反對無異」<br />\n<br />\n2. 有關智慧燈柱的撥款<br />\n係包括係「2019-20 財政年度基本工程儲備基金整體撥款」入面<br />\n總目710 分目A007GX的第64項(下方文件第733頁)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/fc/pwsc/papers/pwsc20181212pwsc-45-1-ec.pdf?fbclid=IwAR1QQ_POGbBY4dTfbcVlC3z5jOr-PkOLkmK5va_PgENWap2VAiUdCUB1RxY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Ffc%2Fpwsc%2Fpapers%2Fpwsc20181212pwsc-45-1-ec.pdf%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1QQ_POGbBY4dTfbcVlC3z5jOr-PkOLkmK5va_PgENWap2VAiUdCUB1RxY&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0cTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=88bc9cf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/fc/pwsc/papers/pwsc20181212pwsc-45-1-ec.pdf?fbclid=IwAR1QQ_POGbBY4dTfbcVlC3z5jOr-PkOLkmK5va_PgENWap2VAiUdCUB1RxY</a><br />\n<br />\n就呢項整體撥款的表決，係今年年頭一月三十日進行<br />\n表決結果係下面連結，大部份泛民議員都係投反對票，包括譚文豪<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/fc/pwsc/results/v201901301.pdf?fbclid=IwAR0Fg0s2HSKu51R3IRYxSWV517goPIZ4FgWdusx