"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5920c9c5cbe5f52105204cec18ed6499241e52b1","tid":1478282,"uid":43939,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"790e854bfe58cf47522f849ee0f296da8bc6d686","tid":1478282,"uid":25797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:13:34.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 到時咪撚再話一國兩制無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:15:33.000Z","msg":"其實以佢地身份 佢地係要堅持一國兩制<br />\n最多提出番實際中共有幾遺反一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"唔係你想點? 你o念住美國會立條法話香港獨立?<br />\n無on9 啦<br />\n要外國勢力幫都要有位入 最名正言順係中英聯合聲明同基本法話有普選<br />\n唔係你試下要求美軍出兵睇下有無人理你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:52:26.000Z","msg":"yes ，先拎左個雙普選番黎再講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8a27d584efb36e5f2f2552e272b70441c2f90c","tid":1478282,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T16:54:02.000Z","msg":"有咁辣得咁辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔可以放過港共"},{"pid":"3fbf35d407524f5663c119cccbac78c6423ac847","tid":1478282,"uid":197640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a261265704bbae89466f8e28379f4f5e7a890fdf","tid":1478282,"uid":81882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"相信應該大家都知道呢件事啦，都推一推先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實琴晚已經想開定但唔記得左<br />\n<br />\n首先再講講咩係<br />\n《香港人權與民主法案》<br />\n<br />\n係2016年時，香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒到訪美國國會，並會見國會及行政當局中國委員會主席克里斯&middot;史密斯（Chris Smith）、聯席主席魯比奧（Marco Rubio）、參議員科頓（Tom Cotton）等國會人員會面。會議後魯比奧和科頓宣佈會提出「香港人權與民主法案」。<br />\n而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong>是美方對涉及鎮壓基本自由的香港或中國大陸的政府官員，設立懲罰機制，包括禁止涉事官員入境美國及凍結其在美國之資產。<br />\n<br />\n但16年後，靜左一排，直到早排G20團隊同大家既努力，令到美國再行動！<br />\n以上COPY至Wikipedia<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實今次 楊岳橋議員 同 郭榮鏗議員 兩位，<br />\n今次到紐約如無意外係會有三場活動！<br />\n<br />\n第一場<br />\n就係美國時間15/8 所參加左由 亞洲協會(ASIA SOCIERY)所舉辦既 EVENT - Perspective on Hong Kong's Protests<br />\n<br />\n即似以下呢段，同應該好多巴打都睇過既片段<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CLYnTTGWT6Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCLYnTTGWT6Y&d=GZKRZRfhFQ75XgsIw24e0cTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=78b4caa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CLYnTTGWT6Y</a><br />\n<br />\n第二場<br />\n美國時間 17/8 星期六<br />\n會參加美國當地港人發起既遊行(原野餐)，<br />\n遊行前都會發言！遊行後都有小組討論<br />\n起點：華埠孔子大廈孔子像<br />\n終點：曼哈頓橋小公園<br />\n<br />\n第三場<br />\n下星期，會到 美國眾議院 同議員商討法案<br />\n<br />\n唔知將來如果成事&hellip;有幾多狗官會享受到呢條法案，忘記美國一切，感受大灣區呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國巴打一齊努力！<br />\n<br />\n所以！見大家話佢地特登唔提雙普或漏左重要既野<br />\n唔緊要！仲有機會！<br />\n<br />\n香港加油！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T20:55:13.000Z","msg":"可以感受西方的獨立司法系統，不枉此生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c3d89c48718367b30c5e523ae09f9ab27bc9d60","tid":1478282,"uid":43204,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T21:52:42.000Z","msg":"dklm 一定賣香港 又話咩一國兩制運作良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4605af9d6924cb1b984b735eeea0e7e7835c04ed","tid":1478282,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T22:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658dfcf1a7abea4c57238347a6f889edfeb18725","tid":1478282,"uid":243847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T23:02:12.000Z","m